id.comment: positive, select if containers that directly follow a while loop.

query.querystr: if i; while w; Select i such that Follows (w, i)

id.comment: positive, select while loops that directly or indirectly follow an if container.

query.querystr: if i; while w; Select w such that Follows* (i, w)

id.comment: positive, select if containers that are a direct parent of another if container

query.querystr: if i, i1; Select i1 such that Parent (i, i1)

id.comment: positive, select read statements that are a direct or indirect child of an if container

query.querystr: if i; read r; Select r such that Parent* (i, r)

id.comment: positive, select while loops that are a direct child of another while loop

query.querystr: while w, w1; Select w1 such that Parent (w, w1)

id.comment: negative, select statements which directly precede an if container

query.querystr: stmt s, if i; Select s such that Follows(s, i)
